Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Ponies' voices{\i0}\N{\i1} fill the night ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Hearth's Warming Eve is{\i0}\N{\i1} here once again. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on everycreature, sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ La la la la la{\i0}\N{\i1} La la la la la la la ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[hesitantly]\N{\i1} ♪ la la la ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everycreature celebrate\Nsame way, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Dragons don't\Ndo pony holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Sure we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I LOVE Hearth's\NWarming Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about friends,\Nand presents, and family,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and.. presents!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also about putting aside\Ndifferences to come together,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,like the Earth ponies, pegasi,\Nand unicorns did
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,on the first holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Is that why you put\Ntheir fire of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To help us remember\Ntheir unity?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,AND 'cause it looks cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite\Nday of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I don't\Nlike the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesdays are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona like any day that\Nis start of Winter Break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Two whole weeks\Nwithout classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How will Ocellus survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Heheh..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll all\Nenjoy the time off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to be home with\Nyour families.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To celebrate your\Nown traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, everycreature!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,School is officially out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Holidays,\Nand we'll see you\Nafter the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And for those of you\Ntraveling outside Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, shouldn't you guys\Nbe getting ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you miss that train,\Nit's a really long walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go pack up, and we'll\Ntake you to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that new bowtie\NI wanted, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have\Nto wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the meantime,\NI'm shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh--what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's ruined;\Nthat's what's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think\Nit was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony was up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Students' Quarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well\Ngive up, whoever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We got ya\Ncornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anypony there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check the\Nback door!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Another decorating party!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anycreature come in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you told us to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear\Nanything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona done packing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The back door's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But whoever did it had\Nto have come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever did{\i1} what{\i0} ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... That...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is so not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And whoever did it\Nran into your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No one came out. And all\Nof you are still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One of you must have done this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would any of you wanna\Nsabotage Hearth's Warming Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! Yak not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona offended by accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this wasn't\Neven on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to give\Nwhoever caused this mess
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a chance to tell the truth\Nand explain themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you did this,\Nraise your hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have to--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike. You can\Nopen your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You ALL can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But since nocreature took\Nresponsibility for this mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you're ALL gonna have\Nto help clean it up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,before you can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! But the holidays!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're cleaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll bring you into my\Noffice one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Honesty is one of\Nthe Elements of Harmony,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we want to give you each a\Nchance to tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And once we find out who\Ndid it, just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna--we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna\Ndo exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] The guilty party\Nwon't be going home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,over Hearth's\NWarming Break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She or he will stay here\Nfor some one-on-one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,friendship lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if none\Nof us confesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no\Nholidays for anycreature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all stay\Nover the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get\Nto the bottom of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to be\Ninterviewed first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats mop duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make a\Ngame out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See who finishes\Ncleaning up first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo!\NYak win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak best at cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's save time and\Ncut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of you did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never do\Nsomething this horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I{\i1} love{\i0} Hearth's\NWarming Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do NOT want to\Nmiss going home for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I didn't even know Changelings\Ncelebrated Hearth's Warming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our favorite holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since Headmare Twilight\Nshared it with us last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave our hive very\Nclear instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[ahem]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Welcome to the traditions\Nand fun of Hearth's Warming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a guide to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoy this celebration\Nof pony history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Families start the holidays\Nby putting the tree up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dive into some Holiday Punch!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just before bed, everypony\Nexchanges gifts."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say how long\Nwe keep doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"And to finish celebrating,\Nyou can build a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And sing carols."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Carols{\i0}\N{\i1} carols carols carols ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You{\i1} might{\i0} have misunderstood\Nthings just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, we may not have\Ndone everything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the way you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But we made our\Nown traditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't wait to do\Nit all again this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ever get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ocellus? Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her I didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Yona tired\Nof waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks ALWAYS home\Nfor holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you celebrate Hearth's\NWarming in Yakyakistan, Yona?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our holiday MUCH better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is called "Snilldar\NFest." Night before,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,yaks gather things to smash,\Nand put them in big pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in morning,\Nwe smash them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In afternoon, we smash them\Nagain. In evening--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So.. it's just about\Nsmashing stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like all your\Nother holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! How griffon\Nget that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This holiday about\Nso much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, for\Nexample.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Most perfect\NSnilldar ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Whole family.{\i0}\N{\i1} Grandpa Grandma Yak,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Yona's Brother Sister{\i0}\N{\i1} Mother Father Yak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} All go to woods,{\i0}\N{\i1} singing Yak Song.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Yak song! Yak song!{\i0}\N{\i1} Not very long! Sing again! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Yak song! Yak song!{\i0}\N{\i1} Not very long! Sing again! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Yak song! Yak song!{\i0}\N{\i1} Not very long! Sing again! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Calves in family pick{\i0}\N{\i1} out perfect Smashing Log.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Then Yaks smash it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Then Yak Family build perfect{\i0}\N{\i1} snow fort... and smash it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Then we hang perfect things{\i0}\N{\i1} on perfect moss pile, and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[All] You smash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What you think Yaks\Nare, barbarians?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Moss pile is for\Nspecial family rituals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, ritual for Yona.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} All Yak family{\i0}\N{\i1} gather around Yona.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} And braid Yona hair{\i0}\N{\i1} for first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So to recap... your holiday\Nis about smashing things,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Two most perfect things\Never, put together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Snilldar Fest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Snilldar to\Nyou too, Yona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cool to learn new\Ntraditions from new friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well one of\Nthese "new friends"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,has gotten us\Nall in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'd better\Nconfess soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ocellus: Sandbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but they said they\Nwant you to go in next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the rush to\Nget home, Smolder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you said, dragons don't\Nreally have holidays, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Meh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] That's so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do{\i1} something{\i0}\Nin the winter for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we do have\N"The Feast of Fire".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Every dragon gets together\Nand tells stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The best one wins a\Npile of gemstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! What story won last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was called "A\NDream Come True."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, now you've\Ngotta tell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, there was\Nthis sad little dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Her name was Scales.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} She lived alone in{\i0}\N{\i1} the wilderness with{\i0}\N{\i1} nothing to eat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} But one night, as she sat{\i0}\N{\i1} alone in a storm, she{\i0}\N{\i1} heard something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} It was the Dragon Lord!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Scales was scared, but the{\i0}\N{\i1} Dragon Lord told her{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} not to be afraid; that he was{\i0}\N{\i1} taking her to the Dragon Lands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} for a great feast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Scales sat with the Dragon{\i0}\N{\i1} Lord's family and friends and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} had the biggest, best dinner{\i0}\N{\i1} of gemstones she'd ever eaten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Then, while the dragons{\i0}\N{\i1} were telling stories,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Scales thought it would be{\i0}\N{\i1} so easy to seize power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} from this feeble and{\i0}\N{\i1} sensitive Dragon Lord.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} She saw her chance{\i0}\N{\i1} and TOOK IT!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} She claimed the{\i0}\N{\i1} bloodstone scepter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and took over the{\i0}\N{\i1} Dragon Lands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bwahahah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ...and forced the Dragon Lord{\i0}\N{\i1} to live out in the cold{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} just as she used to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a horrible story!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe to you..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But dragons like\Nhearing about weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,kind creatures\Ngetting defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rainbow Dash] Silverstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you tell\Nthem you did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You already live\Nin Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying here over\Nbreak is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,School of Friendship good place\Nfor pony to have pony holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd still rather spend it\Nwith my family at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That reminds me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the BEST\Nholiday story ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called "The Day My\NHearth's Warming Doll
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost Fell into the Fire!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[All] Ohhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Just before we went to{\i0}\N{\i1} bed, my mom, my dad,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and my sister all put our{\i0}\N{\i1} Hearth's Warming Dolls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} up on the mantle, just{\i0}\N{\i1} like we do every year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} But THIS year...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I put my doll too close{\i0}\N{\i1} to the edge and it FELL!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[slowly] NOOOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My doll hit the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,BUT! It could have\Ngone in the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you told it\Nreally well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was a Hearth's\NWarming miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Smolder, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona, Twilight's\Nwaiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The last two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So if neither one of them\Nconfesses, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're never going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be here forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't miss the Three\NDays of Freedom Celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does that last?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be only ONE day, but\Nnow to commemorate our escape
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Storm King,\Nwe're adding two more\Ndays of awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm! Queen Novo had these\Nmade for the Mt. Aris
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,board of tourism. To\Nexplain it all to guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We'll spend the first{\i0}\N{\i1} night in Seaquestria,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} thanking the ocean{\i0}\N{\i1} for protecting us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} from the Storm King.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Sea-dancing, whale-singing,{\i0}\N{\i1} shell-stringing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Lots of "ings."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The second day will{\i0}\N{\i1} be on Mt. Aris,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} with sky dancing,{\i0}\N{\i1} and a wind song{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} in the Harmonizing{\i0} Heights
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to celebrate the Storm{\i0}\N{\i1} King's defeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Then the third day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} everycreature will party{\i0}\N{\i1} together, on land AND sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Grandparents and parents{\i0}\N{\i1} and sisters, uncles,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} brothers, acquaintances,{\i0}\N{\i1} neighbours and cousins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} And at the end of the night,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Queen Novo is going to{\i0}\N{\i1} give out presents!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Hold on. Cousins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your aunt's and\Nuncle's children?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, part of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Oh, you're teasing\Nus again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing neither\None of you confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmare Twilight\Nsay wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're changing their\Nminds about sending us home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Face it. We're stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But, but, I\NHAVE to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom makes the\Nbest kelp fritters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so\Ncool about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We just show it\Ndifferently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,More like you don't\Nshow it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What pony getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it wasn't\Njust one prankster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there were\Nthree of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're trying to hide\Nyour guilt by not being upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It does make sense..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe whoever did it is\Nonly pretending to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To throw us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? But I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ocellus,\Nyou know you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I SAID stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what the\Nholidays are about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you call\Nthem, or how you celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how\Nlucky you all are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,With your stories about\Nsharing, and kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting together\Nwith everycreature
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that you care about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Griffons do\Nthat too, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Some holiday\Nabout a moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Blue Moon Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The one time of year\Nwhen Griffons are nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as nice as we can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Families get together to{\i0}\N{\i1} eat and then complain{\i0}\N{\i1} about the food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} And give each other{\i0}\N{\i1} presents they don't like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} And mostly just try not{\i0}\N{\i1} to yell at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least you get\Nto be with your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't have a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar:{\i1} What about{\i0}\N{\i1} Grandpa Gruff?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallus:{\i1} That's just his name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} He's not anygriff's{\i0}\N{\i1} actual grandpa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I felt like I never had{\i0}\N{\i1} a place in Griffonstone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I came here,\Nand well, met all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't want to\Ngo home for the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Griffon mess\Nup decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I put goo powder in\Nthe Fire of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't Ocellus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you ruin\Nthings for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't plan to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just figured if I\Nmade a mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,our teachers would make\Nus stay to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be together\Na little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. It worked, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When Headmare Twilight\Nthreatened to cancel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,winter break, that\Nmeant I would get to\Nbe with all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,through the entire holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you\Nadmitting this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated seeing all you fighting\Nand blaming each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the opposite of what\NALL your holidays mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Except maybe yours, Smolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep all of you from\Nthe happiness of your homes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and families just\Nbecause I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you won't\Nhave to tell our teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We kinda guessed\Nit was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But we wanted to give you\Nthe chance to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud that you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm glad to see you've\Nbeen paying attention
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in Professor Applejack's\Nhonesty classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still gonna\Nhave to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And stay over break for\Nextra friendship lessons,\Nby yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona stay also!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess pony holidays\Ncan't be that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can finally\Nknow what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to spend Hearth's Warming with\Nfriends who care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they don't really\Nneed any extra lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you obviously know\Nthat Hearth's Warming
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is about coming\Ntogether, I'd be honored
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,if all of you would\Njoin my friends as guests
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,at our holiday table.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After we finish cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this reminds\Nme of another story!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Time I Almost Spilled\NGrape Juice on the White Couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have a\Ndepressing ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure pony\Nstories work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Gallus want Yona\Nbraid feathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uuuh. Pass.
